# 📊 Analisis Lengkap Project BizKit POS

## Ringkasan Project

**BizKit POS** adalah aplikasi **Point of Sale (Kasir)** berbasis web dengan arsitektur **full-stack terpisah (decoupled)**:

| Komponen | Teknologi | Direktori |
|----------|-----------|-----------|
| **Backend (API)** | Go (Golang) + Gin Framework + GORM + MySQL | `bizkit-api/` |
| **Frontend (Web)** | React 19 + Vite + Tailwind CSS | `bizkit-web/` |

Komunikasi antara frontend dan backend menggunakan **REST API** dengan autentikasi **JWT (JSON Web Token)**.

---

## 🔧 BACKEND (`bizkit-api`)

### Arsitektur & Struktur Folder

```
bizkit-api/
├── main.go              ← Entry point, routing, CORS config
├── config/
│   └── database.go      ← Koneksi MySQL (GORM), AutoMigrate, Seeder
├── controllers/         ← 15 controller (business logic)
├── models/              ← 6 file model (17 struct/tabel)
├── middleware/
│   └── auth.go          ← JWT Auth & Role-based middleware
├── dtos/
│   └── auth_dto.go      ← Data Transfer Objects untuk login
├── utils/
│   └── jwt.go           ← Generate & Validate JWT token
├── uploads/             ← Folder penyimpanan file upload
└── .env                 ← Konfigurasi environment
```

### Teknologi Backend

| Library | Versi | Fungsi |
|---------|-------|--------|
| `gin-gonic/gin` | v1.12 | HTTP Web Framework (routing, middleware, JSON binding) |
| `gorm.io/gorm` | v1.31 | ORM untuk database (query builder, relasi, migration) |
| `gorm.io/driver/mysql` | v1.6 | Driver MySQL untuk GORM |
| `golang-jwt/jwt/v5` | v5.3 | Pembuatan & validasi JWT token |
| `golang.org/x/crypto` | v0.48 | Password hashing dengan bcrypt |
| `gin-contrib/cors` | v1.7 | Konfigurasi Cross-Origin Resource Sharing |
| `joho/godotenv` | v1.5 | Membaca file [.env](file:///d:/laragon/www/belajar/bizkit/bizkit-api/.env) |

### Database & Model (ERD)

```mermaid
erDiagram
    User ||--o{ Role : "has"
    User ||--o{ Outlet : "belongs to"
    Order ||--o{ User : "created by"
    Order ||--o{ Outlet : "from"
    Order ||--o{ PaymentMethod : "paid with"
    Order ||--|{ OrderItem : "has many"
    OrderItem ||--o{ Product : "item is"
    Product ||--o{ Category : "belongs to"
    Product ||--o{ Brand : "belongs to"
    Product ||--o{ Unit : "measured in"
    Product ||--|{ ProductVariant : "has variants"
    Product ||--|{ ProductPrice : "has prices"
    ProductVariant ||--o{ Variant : "links to"
    Variant ||--|{ VariantOption : "has options"
    ProductPrice ||--o{ PriceCategory : "for category"
    Shift ||--o{ User : "by"
    Attendance ||--o{ User : "by"
```

#### Daftar Tabel (17 tabel)

| No | Tabel | Deskripsi | Field Utama |
|----|-------|-----------|-------------|
| 1 | `roles` | Hak akses (Owner, Superuser, Kasir) | name, permissions (JSON) |
| 2 | `outlets` | Data outlet/cabang | name, logo |
| 3 | `users` | Pengguna sistem | name, email, username, password (bcrypt), role_id, outlet_id |
| 4 | `categories` | Kategori produk | name |
| 5 | `brands` | Merek produk | name |
| 6 | `units` | Satuan (Pcs, Kg, Liter) | name |
| 7 | `products` | Data produk | name, SKU, description, image, price, status, has_variant, is_favorite |
| 8 | `variants` | Grup varian (Level Pedas, Ukuran) | name, min_choice, max_choice, status |
| 9 | `variant_options` | Pilihan varian (Pedas, Sedang) | name, price_add |
| 10 | `product_variants` | Pivot product ↔ variant | product_id, variant_id |
| 11 | `price_categories` | Kategori harga (Gojek, Shopee) | name |
| 12 | `product_prices` | Harga khusus per kategori harga | product_id, price_category_id, price |
| 13 | `payment_methods` | Metode pembayaran (Tunai, QRIS) | name, status |
| 14 | `orders` | Transaksi penjualan | order_number, customer_name, total_qty, total_amount, discount, status |
| 15 | `order_items` | Detail item per transaksi | product_id, qty, price, subtotal |
| 16 | `promotions` | Promo & voucher | name, type, promo_target, condition_type, start/end_date, max_usage |
| 17 | `shifts` | Kas masuk/keluar | description, type, amount_in, amount_out, balance |
| 18 | `attendances` | Absensi karyawan | photo, check_in_time, check_out_time, date |

> **Catatan**: Semua tabel menggunakan **Soft Delete** (`deleted_at`) sehingga data tidak benar-benar terhapus dari database.

### Autentikasi & Keamanan

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Frontend (React)
    participant API as Backend (Go/Gin)
    participant DB as MySQL

    Client->>API: POST /api/auth/login {username, password}
    API->>DB: Cari user berdasarkan username
    DB-->>API: User data + Role + Outlet
    API->>API: Verifikasi password (bcrypt)
    API->>API: Generate JWT Token (24 jam)
    API-->>Client: {token, user: {id, username, role, outlet_name}}
    Note over Client: Simpan token di localStorage

    Client->>API: GET /api/master/products (Header: Bearer token)
    API->>API: AuthMiddleware: Validasi JWT
    API->>API: Set context: userID, username, role
    API->>DB: Query data
    DB-->>API: Hasil query
    API-->>Client: JSON response
```

**Fitur keamanan:**
- Password di-hash menggunakan **bcrypt** (tidak disimpan plaintext)
- JWT token berlaku **24 jam**, menggunakan algoritma **HS256**
- Middleware [AuthMiddleware](file:///d:/laragon/www/belajar/bizkit/bizkit-api/middleware/auth.go#13-44) memvalidasi setiap request ke route `/api/*`
- Middleware [RoleMiddleware](file:///d:/laragon/www/belajar/bizkit/bizkit-api/middleware/auth.go#45-56) tersedia untuk pengaturan akses berdasarkan role
- CORS dikonfigurasi hanya mengizinkan `localhost:5173` dan `localhost:5174`

