## 🔗 Hubungan Frontend ↔ Backend

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph Frontend - React
        A[Login Page] -->|POST /api/auth/login| Z
        B[Products Page] -->|GET /api/master/products| Z
        C[Form Produk] -->|POST/PUT /api/master/products| Z
        D[Laporan] -->|GET /api/reports/sales| Z
        E[Trend] -->|GET /api/reports/trend| Z
        F[User Page] -->|GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /api/users| Z
    end

    Z[Axios HTTP Client<br>+ JWT Bearer Token]

    subgraph Backend - Go Gin
        Z -->|JSON| G[Gin Router]
        G --> H[Auth Middleware]
        H --> I[Controllers]
        I --> J[GORM - Models]
        J --> K[(MySQL Database)]
    end
```

**Pola komunikasi:**
1. Frontend mengirim request HTTP via **Axios** dengan header `Authorization: Bearer <token>`
2. Backend memvalidasi token via **AuthMiddleware**
3. Controller memproses request (CRUD via GORM)
4. Response dikembalikan dalam format **JSON**

