## 🏗️ Seed Data (Data Awal)

Saat server pertama kali berjalan, [database.go](file:///d:/laragon/www/belajar/bizkit/bizkit-api/config/database.go) otomatis membuat:

| Data | Nilai |
|------|-------|
| **3 Role** | Owner (all access), Superuser (all access), Kasir (POS + reports) |
| **1 Outlet** | "Dagashi" |
| **1 User** | username: `ownerdemo`, password: `ownerdemo`, role: Owner |
| **2 Metode Pembayaran** | Tunai, QRIS |

